{"tid":1537642,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"SONY 手機業務會否就此玩完？香港手機部門即將解散","createTime":"2019-09-04T03:57:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T15:36:20.000Z","uid":141060,"like":7,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"d8ff9a4fa6575465c7736a87bcfd502a7ce9734b","tid":1537642,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T03:57:39.000Z","msg":"SONY 手機近年的銷量真係大不如前，就算最新的 Xperia 1 雖然擁有靚仔的外型，至過仍未能扭轉形勢，而更壞的消息於近期出現。就是 SONY 將會結束 SONY Mobile 香港的業務，究竟對 SONY 手機有什麼影響？<br />\n相信大家有玩開智能手機的玩家，對 SONY 手機都一點不陌生，但大家又點睇 SONY 手機？SONY 手機於市場敗北的原因，主要是在設計﹑功能及規格都與其他大品牌的旗艦手機有一段距離， 導致消費者轉頭其他品牌。雖然 SONY 手機於近年面對這個問題，不過仍然在香港有一定的市場佔有率，相當最大功勞都是 SONY Mobile 團隊的努力。不過近日傳出 SONY 打算將手機部門整合，合併到 SONY 品牌旗下，並於9月底解散香港手機部門。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.price.com.hk//space/news/images/20190902/f29ecc8341b77930f81b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.price.com.hk%2F%2Fspace%2Fnews%2Fimages%2F20190902%2Ff29ecc8341b77930f81b.jpg&h=e00a1422&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n小編個人認為關閉香港的手機部門，對 SONY 手機來講，除了可以減省資源外，對香港的手機業務來講未見有什麼幫助。由於一向以來 SONY 手機都要靠香港手機部門積極的市場策略來維持，日後歸入 SONY 旗下，相信資源及人手方面將會大減，加上產品沒有新的突破，日後難以企穩香港市場。而據消息稱，下月於 IFA 2019 上發佈的新 Xperia 手機將是香港 SONY 首款產品，介時就可以看到在沒有手機部門的情況玩又會有什麼分別，相信各大品牌都看準這個機會來搶佔 SONY 手機的份額！"},{"pid":"2ec2584138f8b65bc7215bba7c9244458412137e","tid":1537642,"uid":123991,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T03:57:45.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c1835bf62bb4224149e836f395fac8c82237bef1","tid":1537642,"uid":109923,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:03:31.000Z","msg":"Xperia 1 雖然擁有靚仔的外型？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edeb6fb06b0cdb97273f952b1b23edf68694deab","tid":1537642,"uid":3076,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:25:04.000Z","msg":"初初D機就靚,而家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4713c87a8cc0a697680247c08c578d1b89ada338","tid":1537642,"uid":43520,"like":18,"dislike":10,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:31:18.000Z","msg":"開頭以為Xperia 1是翻身之作<br />\n點知都是好失望, 真心覺得sony唔好再出手機"},{"pid":"c7fb27365f3ed9e9c0aa48a6f3b9bbbc178ea6f6","tid":1537642,"uid":21378,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:36:24.000Z","msg":"21:9 好長. 小眾人先會接受. <br />\n冇咗一部份市場. &nbsp;"},{"pid":"a7c1b946cbfba81c82e39cb17be00a6f4f519c94","tid":1537642,"uid":10717,"like":5,"dislike":21,"score":-16,"quote":{"pid":"4713c87a8cc0a697680247c08c578d1b89ada338","tid":1537642,"uid":43520,"like":18,"dislike":10,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:31:18.000Z","msg":"開頭以為Xperia 1是翻身之作<br />\n點知都是好失望, 真心覺得so